{"tid":982814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥高通每手機收58元專利 蘋果:似被槍指頭","createTime":"2019-01-15T12:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T13:18:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0416899fef2e1f1c52cc843bcfffcbf0bb5e780f","tid":982814,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/01/15/2039039_5a4fd31213ead8ad8a467bece3139d9a_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F01%2F15%2F2039039_5a4fd31213ead8ad8a467bece3139d9a_320.jpg&h=48e3c029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果公司與美國晶片製造商高通(Qualcomm)的專利糾紛持續。蘋果營運總監(COO)威廉斯(Jeff Williams)批評，高通對每部手機收取7.5美元(58.5港元)費用，是一種不公平的商業行為。<br />\n<br />\n威廉斯在美國聯邦貿易委員會(FTC)針對高通的反壟斷審判中作證稱，高通對每部手機收取7.5美元，雖然聽起來不是很多，但蘋果正在銷售數以億計的手機，這將使該筆費用達到每年10億美元(78億港元)，認為高通濫用其在智能手機領域的統治地位，形容蘋果「被槍指着頭部」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2039039/%E6%96%A5%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9A%E6%AF%8F%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%B658%E5%85%83%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9+%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%3A%E4%BC%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%A7%8D%E6%8C%87%E9%A0%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2039039%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2580%259A%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2594%25B658%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%2B%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%253A%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A0%25AD&d=YyosyXkv3krQ3%2BbqA6FPNP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=51ddb892\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2039039/%E6%96%A5%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9A%E6%AF%8F%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%B658%E5%85%83%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9+%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%3A%E4%BC%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%A7%8D%E6%8C%87%E9%A0%AD</a>"},{"pid":"855d132ebf8dfbc2120fffb3e63bd875e93ff21a","tid":982814,"uid":49664,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"